---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - The Davinci Project" description="Learn about The Davinci Project and our mission.">
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>About The Davinci Project</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Digital asset transfer escrow protocol providing reliability and safety in an unsafe world.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>The Davinci Project has re-launched under new management with a clear mission: to provide a secure, reliable, and transparent digital asset transfer escrow protocol.</p>
      <p>We believe that crypto is a vaccine against tyranny. Our protocol ensures that digital assets can be transferred safely and securely, providing trust in an often uncertain digital landscape.</p>
      
      <h2>Our Vision</h2>
      <p>We envision a world where digital asset transfers are as reliable as traditional banking, but with the transparency and security that only blockchain technology can provide.</p>
      <p>Our escrow protocol acts as a trusted intermediary, ensuring that both parties in a transaction can have confidence that the transfer will complete as agreed.</p>
      
      <h2>Our Team</h2>
      <p>The Davinci Project is managed by a team of experienced professionals in blockchain technology, cybersecurity, and financial services. Our combined expertise allows us to build and maintain a protocol that meets the highest standards of security and reliability.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    padding: 8rem 0 4rem;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg-primary) 0%, var(--bg-secondary) 100%);
  }
  
  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }
  
  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }
  
  .subtitle {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 600px;
  }
  
  .content-section {
    padding: 4rem 0;
  }
  
  .content-section h2 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }
  
  .content-section p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .page-hero {
      padding: 7rem 0 3rem;
    }
    
    h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
    
    .container {
      padding: 0 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
